<HEADLINE>
MAN FOR ALL SEASONS: JEWISH SANTA BRINGS JOY TO CHILDREN
</HEADLINE>
 
(Attention editors: Corrects headline, takes out time.) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Will also move in the ``n'' California news file.) 
