<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-23 13:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4132 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SIZE-WAR-ART-BOS &LR;      12-23 1581
