   ..........................................
</P>
<P>
   Everyone's talking about Harold Evans' epic work, ``The American
Century,'' which captures the great events, personalities and
movements of the past 100 years.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times Syndicate is offering to newspapers short
100-word excerpts _ WITH ART! Use one a day in 1999, or compile
them to form weekly or monthly specials.
</P>
