<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-23 14:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4273 &Cx1f; tab-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYTBOOK-SINGER-NYTSF     12-23 1236
