   Maggie Stark of Azle, Texas, would like a recipe for crustless
quiche. The one she misplaced came from a magazine published
between 1981 and 1984, possibly ``Good Housekeeping'' or ``Better
Homes and Gardens.''
</P>
<P>
   Frances Hall of Fort Worth would like a recipe for cranberry
salad that includes cranberries, oranges, apples and nuts.  &QL;
