<HEADLINE>
THREE AIDS VACCINES SHOW PROMISE, U.S. RESEARCHER SAYS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For release Sunday, Dec. 27)   With AIDS-VACCINE)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By ERIC ROSENBERG  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
