American-Statesman)
</P>
<P>
   FBN-STODA-COLUMN _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ The mother said her
son made the call every week. The mother knew well enough, though,
that her telephone would ring later rather than sooner back in Port
Arthur, Texas, during football season if that son's team had lost a
game. Allene Johnson, 77, who died Sunday, understood and loved
that about her boy, Jimmy, who went about his business _ remember
that word _ Monday night in Pro Player Stadium as head coach of the
Dolphins. (Stoda, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   COLLEGE BASKETBALL
</P>
<P>
   BKC-NOTEBOOK _ College basketball notebook. (Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
