<HEADLINE>
KEY RATES 
</HEADLINE>
  (mk) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the daily key rates from The New York Times.
</P>
<P>
   -------------------Wednesday-----Tuesday---Year Ago
</P>
<P>
   PRIME RATE ---------- 7.75 ------ 7.75 ------- 8.50
</P>
<P>
   DISCOUNT RATE ------- 4.50 ------ 4.50 ------- 5.00
</P>
<P>
   FEDERAL FUNDS(x) ---- 4.63 ------ 4.63 ------- 5.08
</P>
<P>
   3-MO. TREAS. BILLS -- 4.46 ------ 4.40 ------- 5.21
</P>
<P>
   6-MO. TREAS. BILLS -- 4.49 ------ 4.43 ------- 5.24
