Delme McIntyre and Carol Clark were more interested in the rough
waters they see ahead for the Los Angeles area.
</P>
<P>
   On April 1, 1999, residents in the 310 area code of Los Angeles
will become the first Californians to get an area code overlay.
When that happens, every call made in the 310 area code will
require callers to dial 1 plus the area code and phone number _
even if the call is to another 310 number next door. By Deborah
Solomon
</P>
