   &UR; SIFE _  &LR; SIFE, a Walnut Creek mutual fund company specializing
in bank stocks, is seeking to sell all or part of the firm to
finance expansion, a company official confirmed. Michael Stead,
SIFE's chief investment officer and manager of its $1.06
billion-asset SIFE Trust Fund, said he expects a sale to take place
by summer. By Sam Zuckerman
